  name: "Esprit de Corps"
  label: null
  type: null
  description: "At 16th level, a Blackjack grants all Blackjacks with whom he is sharing\
    \ one or more teamwork feats through the Blackjack tactics ability a +2 morale\
    \ bonus on attack rolls, ability checks, skill checks, and saving throws. Each\
    \ affected Blackjack increases this bonus by 1 if another affected Blackjack has\
